Package lexparse

Interface KnightCodeListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    KnightCodeBaseListener
    public interface KnightCodeListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by KnightCodeParser.
